For the cognoscenti: I am including classical general relativity with a
 cosmological constant in the 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

standard model
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 for rhetorical purposes.
 This does not exactly match standard particle physics usage of the term
 though, despite the famous difficulties of quantum gravity, it is consistent
 to include general relativity as a low energy effective field theory (see,
