LatexCommand citep
key "Barbieri2000,Blanchet2012,Buchmuller2005,Buchmuller2005a,BuchmÃƒÅ’ller2013329,Canetti2012a,Davidson2008,Fong2012,Giudice2004,Luty1992,Pilaftsis2009"

\end_inset

.
